org.jbei.ice.lib.folder.collection

Class CollectionEntries

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.lib.folder.collection.CollectionEntries

  • public class CollectionEntries
extends Object
    Represents entries contained within a specified collection filtered by the permissions available to the person retrieving the entries
    Author:
    Hector Plahar

        Retrieves entries shared with user.
        Parameters:
        field - sort field
        asc - sort order ascending if true, descending if false
        offset - paging parameter start
        limit - maximum number of entries to retrieve
        filter - optional text to filter entries by
